oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Results of yield trails with spring barley
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Jensen, Scientist-VCU_testing Jakob Willas
Deneken, Scientist Gerhard
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cereals, pulses and oilseeds
oai_dc:dc.dc:description:
Variety trails concerning 132 varieties in organic and conventional growing systems has been conducted.
Data of yield, disease susceptibility, growth characteristics and quality can be found on this web page. Additional links for further results and administrative data can be found as well.
